# Testing Rules

## Required Tests
- Unit tests for all domain logic and data layer
- Widget tests for all pages and complex widgets
- Integration tests for critical user flows

## Standards
- Use mocktail for mocking (NOT mockito)
- Tests must be deterministic — mock all I/O
- Async: use pump/pumpAndSettle, never real timers
- Group related tests with group()
- Descriptive test names: "should [expected] when [condition]"

## File Structure
- Test files mirror lib/ structure
- test/unit/, test/widget/, test/integration/ OR
- test/<feature>/presentation/, test/<feature>/domain/, test/<feature>/data/

## Coverage
- Minimums defined in tooling/coverage.yaml
- CI fails if coverage regresses below threshold
